    <p>Paris Baguette’s</p>
    <p>Limited Edi­tion Crois­sants</p>
    <p>Bak­ery cafe chain Paris Baguette is cel­e­brat­ing the na­tion’s birth­day with three limited-edi­tion crois­sants ($5.50 each) in these flavours: Milo, Rose Ban­dung and Con­densed Milk. It also has a “buy five, get five free pas­tries” deal for in-store and take­away or­ders. The pas­tries avail­able for the pro­mo­tion in­cludes Paris Baguette’s Crois­sant, Pain au Cho­co­lat, Mini Crois­sant as well as the limited-edi­tion crois­sants.</p>
    <p>All op­er­at­ing Paris Baguette out­lets Var­i­ous</p>
    <p>Limited-edi­tion crois­sants:</p>
    <p>Till Sun; buy five, get five free pas­tries deal: Till Aug 17</p>
    <p>www.paris­baguettesg.com</p>
    <p>Lo­cal De­lights At The Or­chard Cafe</p>
    <p>The Or­chard Cafe will serve lo­cal del­i­ca­cies such as Sig­na­ture</p>
    <p>Laksa Chee Cheong Fun with Tem­pura Prawns and Sin­ga­pore</p>
    <p>Chilli Crabs with Honey Pomelo Pulp. Guests may pair the ap­pe­tis­ers with dishes like Freshly-made Tho­sai Masala Co­conut Chut­ney and Tomato Chut­ney and Ren­dang Rib-eye Steak. Desserts in­clude Sig­na­ture Mango</p>
    <p>Cake and Durian Basque Burnt Cheese­cake.</p>
    <p>The Or­chard Cafe, Or­chard Ho­tel Sin­ga­pore, 442 Or­chard Road</p>
    <p>Or­chard Na­tional Day Un­lim­ited Plated Lunch: Noon - 2.30pm; Na­tional Day Un­lim­ited</p>
    <p>High Tea: 3 - 5pm; Na­tional Day Un­lim­ited Plated Din­ner: To­day - Sun & Aug 14 & 15, 6 - 10pm Na­tional Day Un­lim­ited Plated Lunch: $55 an adult; Na­tional Day Un­lim­ited High Tea: $42; Na­tional Day Un­lim­ited Plated Din­ner: $55; 30 per cent off lunch & high tea from to­mor­row -</p>
    <p>Mon & Aug 15 & 16; chil­dren be­low five years old dine for free, those aged five - 12 pay half-price 6739-6565</p>
    <p>E-mail or­chard­cafe.ohs@ mil­len­ni­umho­tels.com</p>
    <p>Limited-Edi­tion Foodie Jig­saw Puz­zle</p>
    <p>De­liv­ery plat­form De­liv­eroo and fast-food chain Burger King have launched a limited-edi­tion</p>
    <p>120-piece A4-size foodie jig­saw puz­zle. It is com­pli­men­tary with ev­ery or­der of the Ren­dang Dou­ble Beef XXL Meal ($11.50) from six out­lets via De­liv­eroo on Na­tional Day. Only 30 sets are up for grabs.</p>
    <p>Burger King out­lets at</p>
    <p>Bukit Ba­tok East Com­mu­nity Club, Jurong Point, Sele­tar Mall, Tampines North Com­mu­nity Club, Viva Busi­ness Park & Yishun Var­i­ous</p>
    <p>Sun</p>
    <p>Na­tional Day Bun­dle At Harry’s</p>
    <p>Pur­chase the bar’s Na­tional Day Bun­dle ($55++ in-store, $55 nett for de­liv­ery) and top up $5.50 for an ex­clu­sive Harry’s glass­ware item. You can buy up to two glasses for each bun­dle. The bun­dle comes with a choice of Flat­bread Pizza, Otah Toasties or Laksa Pop­corn Chicken, and two pints of Harry’s Premium Lager or Sin­ga­pore Sling (for dine-in) or a 1-litre bag of</p>
    <p>Harry’s Premium Lager or two DIY Sin­ga­pore Sling Cock­tail pouches (for de­liv­ery).</p>
    <p>Harry’s out­lets Var­i­ous Till Aug 31 str.sg/Jn6e</p>
    <p>Lavo’s Na­tional Day Spe­cials</p>
    <p>Dur­ing the Na­tional Day week, Ital­ian restau­rant Lavo is of­fer­ing spe­cials for din­ner, in­clud­ing starters such as fresh Com­posed Oys­ters and Steam Buns fea­tur­ing Pork Belly, Cab­bage Slaw and Cal­abrian Chili Aioli. Din­ers can also dig into live crab ($88++) with a choice of black pep­per or chilli. Dessert is Sin­ga­pore Sling Sor­bet. Reser­va­tions are re­quired.</p>
    <p>Lavo Ital­ian Restau­rant & Rooftop Bar, Tower 1, 10 Bayfront Av­enue Bayfront</p>
    <p>Till Mon 6688-8591 E-mail lavo.reser­va­tions@ marin­abaysands.com</p>
    <p>Koma El­e­vates Lo­cal Dishes</p>
    <p>ren­di­tions of lo­cal dishes such as Nasi Lemak Roll ($26++) and Crispy Yel­low­tail Kama. Toast to the oc­ca­sion with Koma’s take on the classic Sin­ga­pore Sling ($22++), which uses Sawan­ot­suru Jyosen Hon­jozo sake and end the evening with Rasp­berry Sin­ga­pura, a crunchy rice crum­ble served with a rasp­berry-based “Sin­ga­pore flag”. Reser­va­tions are re­quired.</p>
    <p>Koma Sin­ga­pore, B1-67 Ma­rina Bay Sands, 2 Bayfront Av­enue Bayfront To­day - Mon 6688-8690 E-mail koma.reser­va­tions@ marin­abaysands.com</p>


